    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "WUNITED\nmenu",
      "TO BEGIN\nProvolone cheese with sliced tomato and red onion\nGarden fresh salad with balsamic vinaigrette\nMAIN COURSE\nChicken with rice enhanced by warm tomato salsa\nBreast of chicken atop a bed of saffron rice\nTomato cream ravioli\nCheese ravioli enhanced by tomato cream sauce\nMarinated beef brisket\nAccompanied by mashed potatoes and green beans\nDESSERT\nTriple chocolate brownie bash\nPRIOR TO ARRIVAL\nContinental breakfast featuring a fruit appetizer,\nbreakfast breads and fruit preserve\nWINES\nOffered with our compliments, Capendieu Chardonnay\nor Georges Dubœuf Cabernet Sauvignon and Chardonnay\nOTHER BEVERAGES\nSTARBUCKS coffee, decaffeinated coffee, tea and\nselected soft drinks are available throughout the flight.\nWe apologize if occasionally your choice is not available.\nJFKEWRIADIORD/BOS-LHR (072-376)\nECONOMY\n310Y021-3\n2006. 054.301.247"
    ],
